#

Red Wine and Herb Beef Gravy

$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Tags:

saucegravybeefwine

Description

A rich and flavorful gravy made with red wine and fresh herbs, perfect for enhancing your beef dishes.

Ingredients

  • beef broth: 2 cups
  • red wine: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • water: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
